<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>IDI </title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="home.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-5 ">
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-6">
                            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0"
                                    class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1"
                                    aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2"
                                    aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-inner mt-5">
                        <!-- <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox" style=" width:100%; height: 500px !important;"> -->
                        <div class="carousel-item active c-item">
                            <!-- <img src="1.png" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="slide 1"> -->
                            <img src="home1.png" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="slide 1">
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block ">
                                <h1>עיצוב הבית</h1>
                                <p>עיצובים חדישים המותאמים לסגנון שלכם שעוצבו על ידי מעצבי הפנים הטובים בארץ</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item c-item">
                            <img src="home2.png" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="slide 2">
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block ">
                                <h1>חווית קניה שלא הכרתם</h1>
                                <p>מאות מוצרים מהמותגים המובילים נגישים לכם בלחיצת כפתור</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item c-item">
                            <img src="home3.png" class="d-block w-100 c-img" alt="slide 3">
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                                <h1>בדיקת המוצר בבית לפני הקניה</h1>
                                <p>בעזרת טכנולוגיית המציאות הרבודה תוכלו להניח את המוצר אצלכם בחדר, בגודלו המדוייק,
                                    ולראות
                                    איך הוא
                                    משתלב בחלל</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
                        data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- sign up botton -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-3">
                <div class="div text-center pt-5 mt-5 pb-5 mb-5">
                    <a href="/signin" class="btn btn-xl shadow" role="button">בואו נתחיל</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="div text-center">
                        <h4 class="h4-fotter-sign">אתם עדיין לא רשומים? <a class="font-weight-bolder"
                                href="/signup">הרשמו
                            </a></h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>




    <!-- bootstrap script -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ENjdO4Dr2bkBIFxQpeoTz1HIcje39Wm4jDKdf19U8gI4ddQ3GYNS7NTKfAdVQSZe"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>